Class MyModel

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
MyModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
public class MyModel extends AbstractTableModel
MyModel is a custom table model that extends AbstractTableModel to provide data for a JTable, representing a list of CD entries. The table supports dynamic row addition, sorting by column, and a boolean display for the "On-Loan" status.
